  "detailed_description": "A FPS with Rogue-like elements. Features a random level generator and collectable items with passive effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Random Level Generator:</strong></h2>Every level of every game you play will be different.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/LevelVar01_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/LevelVar02_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/LevelVar04_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Foes:</strong></h2>These are the enemies who will kill you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Zombie01_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Soldier02_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Boss02_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons:</h2></strong><br>These are your tools of survival.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Pistol_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Rifle_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Sniper_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/RocketLauncher_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items:</h2></strong><br>Collect these to improve your chances at survival. Item effects can stack multiple times increasing their effect.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Health: Recover 10 HP.<br></li><li>Heart: Increase your Max Health value by 10 points.<br></li><li>Shield: Increase your Max Energy Shield value by 10 points.<br></li><li>Incendiary Rounds: Set your foes on fire for 4 seconds; Foes burn for 1 HP per stack per second; Foes already on fire burn for an additional 10% of your total stack value per hit.<br></li><li>Biohazard: Chance to leave a poisonous cloud on hit; Foes within radius are damaged for 5 HP per stack per second; Radius is 5 feet + 2 feet per additional stack.<br></li><li>Lightning Bolt: Increase your movement speed by 5% of your current value.<br></li><li>Armor: Increase your damage reduction by 3% per stack.<br></li><li>Dagger: Increase your life leech by 10% per stack.<br></li><li>Revive: Gain an extra life; Each revival halves your current Max Health value per use.<br></li><li>Magnet: Collectibles are now attracted to you within radius; Radius is 5 feet per stack. <br></li><li>Over Clocked Shield: Reduce your shield delay and shield recovery by 15%.<br></li><li>Medic: Increase your health regeneration by 1 HP per stack per second.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Items_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ammo:</h2></strong><br>Don't run out!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1603460/extras/Ammo_Small.PNG?t=1619766362\" /></span>",
